e%2C%20Ishimoto%20credits%20this%20heat%20protectant%20hair%20spray%20with%20protecting%20%26quot%3Bthe%20color%20from%20fading%20from%20styling%20tools.%26quot%3B%20Plus%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20contains%20a%20humidity%20protectant%20shield%20to%20reduce%20frizz%20and%20emollients%20to%20smooth%2C%20shine%20and%20soften%20hair.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20Drugstore%3Cp%3ELooking%20for%20a%20solid%20drugstore%20option%20for%20the%20best%20heat%20protectant%20that's%20stylist-approved%3F%20Consider%20the%20OGX%20Protecting%20%2B%20Silk%20Blowout%20Quick%20Drying%20Thermal%20Spray%2C%20which%20protects%20hair%20against%20heat%20as%20high%20as%20450%20degrees.%20Per%20Ishimoto%2C%20this%20heat-protectant%20hair%20spray%20%26quot%3Bhelps%20to%20cut%20hair%20drying%20time%20while%20protecting%20hair%20from%20heat%20damage.%26quot%3B%20He%20continues%2C%20telling%20INSIDER%2C%20%26quot%3Bhydrolyzed%20silk%20%26amp%3B%20quinoa%20will%20keep%20hair%20looking%20healthy%20and%20damage-free.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20Blowouts%3Cp%3ELike%20all%20Ouai%20products%2C%20this%20heat%20protection%20spray%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20specially%20formulated%20to%20protect%20hair%20from%20heat%20damage%20caused%20by%20blowouts%20and%20styling%20tools%20%E2%80%94%20smells%20absolutely%20divine.%20The%20nozzle%20is%20super%20effective%20and%20evenly%20coats%20the%20hair%20so%20well%20that%20you%20wind%20up%20using%20less%20product.%20It%20definitely%20makes%20the%20hair%20much%20shinier%20and%20humidity-proof.%20This%20can%20be%20considered%20the%20best%20heat%20protectant%20spray%20for%20both%20fine%20and%20thick%20hair%20alike.%20It%20will%20add%20volume%2C%20shine%2C%20and%20a%20smell%20so%20divine%20you'll%20want%20to%20spray%20it%20all%20over.%20Just%20make%20so%20to%20position%20the%20bottle%20at%20least%20six%20inches%20from%20your%20head%20as%20you%20apply%3A%C2%A0%20it%20applies%20pretty%20heavily%20if%20you%20don't.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20Frizzy%20Hair%3Cp%3EFrizzy%20hair%2C%20do%2C%20care%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that's%20where%20the%20Color%20Wow%20Dream%20Coat%20Anti-Humidity%20Hair%20Treatment%20comes%20into%20play.%20The%20heat-protectant%20hair%20spray%2C%20which%20features%20a%20weightless%2C%20water-like%20formula%2C%20can%20fight%20frizz%20for%20days%20(even%20between%20washes!).%C2%A0%20Although%20you%20have%20to%20make%20sure%20to%20section%20off%20your%20hair%20as%20your%20spraying%20this%20product%20in%20order%20to%20evenly%20coat%20it%2C%20it%20really%20holds%20your%20style%20(while%20also%20blocking%20frizz%20and%20keeping%20your%20strands%20looking%20and%20feeling%20silky-smooth!)%20for%20days%20on%20end.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20Vegan%3Cp%3EBeauty%20fans%20shopping%20for%20the%20best%20heat%20protectants%20are%20most%20likely%20familiar%20with%20R%2BCo%20already%2C%20but%20the%20brand%20has%20recently%20launched%20a%20couture%20line%3A%20R%2BCo%20Bleu.%20This%20mist%20from%20the%20line%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20is%20phenomenal.%20It%20offers%20heat%20protection%20up%20to%20450%20degrees%20and%20leaves%20the%20hair%20feeling%20flexible%20so%20that%20you%20can%20update%20your%20'do%20over%20the%20next%20few%20days.%20Its%20vegan%20formula%20%E2%80%94%20which%20pulls%20double%20duty%20as%20a%20humidity%20shield%20%E2%80%94%20works%20well%20on%20all%20hair%20types%2C%20as%20it%20coats%20each%20strand%20evenly%20and%20provides%20a%20texture%20that%20isn't%20super%20drying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20Fine%20Hair%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20acting%20as%20a%20heat%20shield%2C%20Living%20Proof's%20Perfect%20Hair%20Day%20Heat%20Styling%20Spray%20almost%20works%20as%20a%20texturizer%20and%20dry%20shampoo.%20As%20such%2C%20it's%20a%20fantastic%20option%20for%20the%20best%20heat%20protectant%20spray%20for%20those%20with%20fine%20hair%20looking%20for%20a%20little%20volume.%20It's%20also%20great%20on%20greasy%20strands%3A%20J