20for%2C%20but%20during%20my%20appointment%20I%20learned%20things%20that%20surprised%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELooking%20back%2C%20I%20wish%20I%20researched%20some%20of%20the%20potential%20risks%20and%20side%20effects%20before%20I%20went.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20years%20of%20trying%20to%20smooth%20my%20forehead%20lines%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ffrownies-review-tried-face-taping-reduce-wrinkles-botox-alternative-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eface-taping%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fbotox-alternative-anti-aging-skincare-products%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eretinol%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20finally%20decided%20to%20book%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fsigns-youre-ready-for-botox-according-to-a-dermatologist-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20Botox%20appointment%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20age%20of%2032.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20sick%20of%20seeing%20my%20fine%20lines%20and%20judging%20my%20past%20self%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhow-to-repair-sun-damaged-skin-according-to-dermatologist-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eneglecting%20sunscreen%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20So%20with%20a%20discount%20code%20in%20hand%2C%20I%20shuffled%20into%20a%20local%20Botox%20clinic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20already%20looked%20up%20the%20price%20tag%20and%20possible%20side%20effects.%20Besides%2C%20because%20I%20write%20about%20skincare%20at%20work%2C%20I%20figured%20I%20already%20had%20the%20basics%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20after%20getting%20briefed%20on%20all%20the%20potential%20risks%20and%20the%20aftercare%20instructions%2C%20there%20were%20some%20things%20that%20I%20wish%20I%20had%20known%20before%20I%20got%20my%20first%20jab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20There's%20a%20small%20chance%20you%20can%20get%20a%20droopy%20eyelid%20%E2%80%94%20for%20weeks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20procedure%2C%20the%20nurse%20practitioner%20had%20me%20sign%20a%20form%20consenting%20to%20all%20possible%20risks%20%E2%80%94%20including%20an%20%26quot%3Beyelid%20droop%2C%26quot%3B%20also%20called%20ptosis.%20About%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.webmd.com%2Feye-health%2Feyelid-droops-after-botox%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E5%25%20of%20patients%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20experience%20this%2C%20according%20to%20WebMD%2C%20with%20the%20number%20dropping%20to%201%25%20with%20more%20experienced%20dermatologists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20NP%20was%20honest%20with%20me%20that%20while%20it's%20never%20happened%20with%20one%20of%20her%20clients%2C%20some%20patients%20of%20the%20clinic%20had%20gotten%20ptosis%20in%20the%20past.%20If%20it%20were%20to%20happen%2C%20it%20would%20take%20about%203-4%20weeks%20to%20improve%20as%20the%20neurotoxin%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fthree-ways-to-make-botox-last-longer-zinc-dosing-brands-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estart%20to%20wear%20off%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20made%20me%20worry%2C%20because%20I%20had%20a%20choir%20performance%2C%20holiday%20parties%2C%20and%20family%20events%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks.%20But%20I%20realized%20that%20there's%20no%20time%20in%20my%20life%20where%20I%20have%20nowhere%20to%20be%20for%20three%20weeks%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20chance%20it.%20Luckily%2C%20that%20side%20effect%20didn't%20happen%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20You%20can%20get%20headaches%2C%20but%20you%20can't%20take%20some%20common%20pain%20relievers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20not%20surprising%2C%20but%20getting%20jabbed%20with%20a%20needle%20about%2020%20times%20all%20over%20your%20forehead%20leads%20to%20mild%20discomfort.%20I%20had%20two%20tiny%20bruises%20on%20my%20forehead%20and%20a%20low-grade%20headache%20two%20days%20after%20the%20shots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20my%20NP%20warned%20me%20to%20avoid%20taking%20blood%20thinners%20like%20ibuprofen%2C%20which%20is%20what%20I%20had%20at%20home%2C%20as%20it%20could%20increase%20bruising.%20I%20ended%20up%20just%20riding%20out%20the%20headache%20because%20I%20was%20too%20lazy%20to%20buy%20Tylenol%2C%20but%20I'll%20stock%20up%20beforehand%20next%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20You%20shouldn't%20work%20out%20or%20drink%20the%20day%20after%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20NP%20advised%20me%20not%20to%20drink%20alcohol%20or%20work%20out%20for%20at%20least%2024%20hours.%20This%20guidance%20varies%20%E2%80%94%20some%20experts%20say%20%3Cu%3Ey%3C%2Fu%3Eou%20can%20do%20moderate%20exercise%20after%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mi-skin.com%2Fblog%2Fwhen-can-i-exercise-after-botox%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20four%20hours%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Others%20say%20to%20avoid%20alcohol%20before%20the%20procedure%20and%20up%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.medicalnewstoday.com%2Farticles%2Fcan-you-drink-alcohol-after-botox%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%2048%20hours%20after%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20plans%20the%20next%20day%20and%20was%20feeling%20a%20little%20burned%20out%20from%20the%20weekend%2C%20so%20it%20was%20a%20nice%20excuse%20to%20do%20nothing.%20Next%20time%2C%20I'll%20make%20sure%20to%20keep%20this%20in%20mind%20so%20I%20don't%20plan%20the%20injections%20around%20an%20event%20or%20workout%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20You%20can't%20do%20Botox%20if%20you're%20pregnant%20or%20trying%20to%20get%20pregnant%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20from%20my%20past%20reporting%20that%20in%20order%20to%20have%20long-term%20results%2C%20you%20need%20to%20be%20consistent%20with%20Botox%20and%20get%20it%20every%203-4%20months%20%E2%80%94%20otherwise%2C%20the%20effects%20fade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20I%20couldn't%20afford%20it%20in%20my%2020s%20and%20was%20so%20indecisive%20about%20it%20once%20I%20could%2C%20I'm%20now%20starting%20treatments%20only%20a%20few%20years%20before%20I%20want%20to%20try%20having%20a%20child.%20But%20I%20learned%20not%20only%20should%20I%20not%20get%20Botox%20while%20pregnant%2C%20I%20should%20steer%20clear%20of%20it%20if%20I%20breastfeed%20and%20even%20when%20I'm%20trying%20to%20conceive%2C%20as%20the%20possible%3Cu%3E%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthline.com%2Fhealth%2Fpregnancy%2Fbotox-while-pregnant%23risks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eeffects%20on%20the%20fetus%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3Eare%20still%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I'll%20continue%20getting%20Botox%20until%20then%2C%20it%20means%20I%20might%20miss%20out%20on%20years%20of%20it%2C%20and%20my%20forehead%20will%20revert%20back%20to%20what%20it%20looked%20like%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20Dr.%20Stacey%20Tull%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fsigns-youre-ready-for-botox-according-to-a-dermatologist-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ea%20dermatologist%20I%20previously%20spoke%20to%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Beven%20deep-set%20lines%20will%20eventually%20disappear%20if%20you%20don't%20allow%20the%20muscles%20to%20crease%20the%20skin%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20it%20just%20might%20take%20longer%20to%20get%20there.%20So%20I%20can%20always%20pick%20up%20where%20I%20left%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHonestly%2C%20it's%20kind%20of%20a%20relief%3A%20I%20can't%20imagine%20booking%20appointments%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20raising%20an%20infant.%20By%20then%2C%20I'm%20sure%20I%20(and%20my%20wallet)%20will%20welcome%20the%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-i-wish-i-knew-before-botox-first-time-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701904441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6570dcec58e7c0c29a2a65d1%3