3ESPICE%20kits%3C%2Fa%3E%20use%20an%20advanced%20electro-optical%20guidance%20and%20the%20inertial%20navigation%20system%2Fglobal%20positioning%20system%20(INS%2FGPS)%20to%20perform%20mid-course%20navigation%20on%20its%20own.%20Rafael%20Advanced%20Defense%20Systems%2C%20which%20manufactures%20the%20kit%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rafael.co.il%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2FSpice-1000-2000.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esays%20in%20a%20fact%20sheet%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20SPICE%20can%20enable%20%26quot%3Bfully%20autonomous%20attack%20missions%20with%20pinpoint%20accuracy.%26quot%3B%20The%20circular%20error%20probability%2C%20it%20asserts%2C%20is%20less%20than%2010%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGarlasco%2C%20who%20served%20as%20the%20Pentagon's%20chief%20of%20high-value%20targeting%20during%20Operation%20Iraqi%20Freedom%2C%20said%20that%20the%20system%20is%20useful%20in%20GPS-denied%20environments%2C%20although%20its%20employment%20in%20Gaza%20is%20surprising%20because%20jamming%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20be%20an%20issue%20there.%20He%20also%20noted%20that%20while%20weapon%20equipped%20with%20SPICE%20may%20be%20extremely%20accurate%2C%20the%20bigger%20issue%20is%20the%20broad%20area%20effects%20and%20the%20potential%20to%20cause%20civilian%20harm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20talking%20about%20a%20densely%20populated%20area%20like%20Gaza%2C%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20certain%20concerns%20about%20collateral%20effects%2C%20particularly%20widespread%20collateral%20effects%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20blast%20overpressure%20at%20the%20site%20of%20a%20Mark%2084%20explosion%20can%20kill%20out%20to%20100%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20aftermath%20of%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike%20in%20Gaza%20on%20December%201%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656a399747f9ecb37d894060%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20aftermath%20of%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike%20in%20Gaza%20on%20December%201%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20Fadi%20Alwhidi%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20pretty%20much%20instant%20death%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20one's%20going%20to%20survive%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELethal%20fragments%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20can%20spread%20as%20far%20as%201%2C200%20feet%2C%20although%20that's%20ultimately%20influenced%20by%20the%20terrain%20%E2%80%94%20a%20building%20adjacent%20to%20the%20blast%20site%20might%20prevent%20shrapnel%20from%20traveling%20farther.%20Still%2C%20there's%20the%20possibility%20of%20secondary%20fragmentation%2C%20or%20pieces%20of%20a%20building%20such%20as%20metal%20and%20cement%20that%20fly%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20been%20dropping%20other%20large%20large%20bombs%20on%20Gaza%20in%20other%20forms%20as%20well.%20The%202%2C000-pound%20Mark%2084%20bomb%20can%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20also%20be%20outfitted%20with%20the%20US-provided%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.af.mil%2FAbout-Us%2FFact-Sheets%2FDisplay%2FArticle%2F104572%2Fjoint-direct-attack-munition-gbu-313238%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJoint%20Direct%20Attack%20Munition%3C%2Fa%3E%20(JDAM)%20kit%2C%20which%20is%20similar%20to%20SPICE%20in%20that%20it%20converts%20unguided%20bombs%20into%20smart%2C%20precision%20munitions%20that%20work%20in%20any%20weather%20condition.%20There%20are%20also%20indications%20Israel%20has%20used%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisraeli-air-force-photos-fighter-aircraft-armed-unguided-weapons-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunguided%20%26quot%3Bdumb%26quot%3B%20bombs%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrian%20Castner%2C%20a%20senior%20crisis%20advisor%20and%20a%20weapons%20investigator%20for%20Amnesty%20International's%20Citizen%20Evidence%20Lab%2C%20said%20the%20employment%20of%20larger%20weapons%20is%20causing%20greater%20damage%20and%20civilian%20casualties%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Israeli%20Air%20Force%20personnel%20working%20with%20a%20JDAM%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6529913955f52b01b35f6a74%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIsraeli%20Air%20Force%20personnel%20working%20with%20a%20JDAM.%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Air%20Force%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20use%20of%20explosive%20weapons%20generally%20in%20populated%20areas%20can%20be%20really%20problematic%20because%20they%20just%20have%20wide%20area%20effects%2C%26quot%3B%20Castner%2C%20a%20former%20explosive%20ordnance%20disposal%20(EOD)%20officer%20in%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Even%20if%20Israel%20identifies%20and%20hits%20an%20intended%20target%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20surrounding%20damage%20that%20they%20do%20either%20to%20infrastructure%20or%20to%20civilians%20is%20much%20greater%20with%20a%20larger%20weapon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Castner%20and%20Garlasco%20acknowledged%20that%20there%20are%20some%20targets%20that%20may%20warrant%20the%20use%20of%20a%202%2C000-pound%20bomb%2C%20like%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-invasion-gaza-hamas-hardest-fighting-underground-tunnels-warfare-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderground%20tunnel%3C%2Fa%3E%20belonging%20to%20Hamas'%20vast%20network%2C%20but%20the%20issue%20is%20that%20widespread%20use%20of%20large%20munitions%20in%20such%20a%20densely%20populated%20area%20can%20spell%20trouble%20and%20raise%20concerns%20that%20the%20choice%20of%20weapon%2C%20while%20accurate%2C%20is%20not%20as%20protective%20of%20civilians%20as%20the%20munitions%20selected%20should%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20how%20widespread%20the%20use%20of%20the%20SPICE%20kits%20have%20been.%20Even%20if%20a%202%2C000-pound%20Mark%2084%20leaves%20a%20large%20crater%2C%20it%20might%20not%20necessarily%20determine%20whether%20that%20bomb%20was%20guided%20by%20a%20SPICE%20or%20a%20JDAM%20kit.%20The%20weapons%20investigators%20explained%20that%20identifying%20which%20was%20used%20involves%20looking%20for%20key%20features%20like%20fragmentation%20and%20remnants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20its%20apparent%20use%20of%20the%20SPICE%20kit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222108%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smoke%20rises%20in%20the%20northern%20Gaza%20Strip%20following%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike%20on%20November%208%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6570a90b7a3c8094d5da2a10%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESmoke%20rises%20in%20the%20northern%20Gaza%20Strip%20following%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike%20on%20November%208%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20short-lived%20truce%20fades%20further%20away%2C%20Israel's%20bombardment%20of%20Gaza%20and%20the%20concurrent%20ground%20invasion%20continues.%20Rear%20Adm.%20Daniel%20Hagari%2C%20an%20IDF%20spokesperson%2C%20said%20at%20a%20Tuesday%20briefing%20that%20the%20military%20has%20struck%20over%2020%2C000%20targets%20in%20the%20coastal%20enclave%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20war%20two%20months%20ago.%20In%20that%20time%2C%20more%20than%2016%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20there%2C%20according%20to%20figures%20from%20the%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Israeli%20officials%20continue%20to%20signal%20%E2%80%94%20as%20they've%20done%20since%20the%20Hamas%20massacre%20that%20killed%20over%201%2C200%20people%20%E2%80%94%20that%20the%20war%20has%20no%20end%20in%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLately%2C%20I%20have%20been%20asked%20whether%20we%20have%20the%20legitimacy%20to%20conti