ch%20out%20for%20before%20trying%20any%20new%20supplement%20or%20longevity%20medication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20You%20could%20risk%20a%20drug%20interaction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESupplements%20can%20interact%20with%20other%20supplements%20and%20prescription%20medications%20in%20potentially%20dangerous%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBill%20Gurley%2C%20principal%20scientist%20in%20the%20National%20Center%20for%20Natural%20Products%20Research%2C%20previously%20told%20Insider%20that%20taking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fmost-dangerous-supplements-natural-herbal-athletic-heart-issues-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupplements%20that%20have%20more%20than%20one%20ingredient%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20like%20opening%20a%20%26quot%3Bpharmacological%20pandora's%20box.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20ingredients%20a%20supplement%20has%2C%20or%20the%20more%20supplements%20you%20take%20simultaneously%2C%20the%20greater%20the%20risk%20for%20an%20adverse%20interaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20supplements%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fsupplements-can-become-lethal-combined-with-prescription-drugs-calcium-iron-2022-5%23everyday-supplements-such-as-calcium-vitamin-k-and-potassium-can-turn-deadly-when-combined-with-prescription-medications-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Einteract%20with%20your%20prescription%20medications%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20potentially%20harmful%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20magnesium%20can%20interact%20with%20antibiotics%2C%20as%20well%20as%20some%20blood%20pressure%20medications%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.webmd.com%2Fvitamins%2Fai%2Fingredientmono-998%2Fmagnesium%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20WebMD%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOmega-3%20supplements%20may%20interact%20with%20blood%20thinning%20medications%20and%20cause%20potentially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lancastergeneralhealth.org%2F-%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Flancaster%2520general%2Fpdfs%2Fhealth%2520care%2520professionals%2Ftrauma%2F2017%2Fomega3%2520fatty%2520acid%2520supplementation%2520and%2520warfarin%2520a%2520lethal%2520combination%2520in%2520traumatic%2520brain%2520injury.ashx%3Fla%3Den%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOmega%252D3%2520fatty%2520acids%2520found%2Cof%2520warfarin%2520and%2520other%2520anticoagulants.%26text%3DCombining%2520omega%252D3%2520fatty%2520acid%2Cat%2520increased%2520risk%2520for%2520bleeding.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elethal%20bleeding%20during%20an%20injury%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%2C%20Dr.%20Andrea%20Maier%2C%20co-director%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20Healthy%20Longevity%20at%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore%2C%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20she%20will%20only%20introduce%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupplement-expert-doesnt-take-supplements-eats-vegan-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20supplement%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20her%20patients%20routine%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20do%20in%20chemistry%20has%20effects%2C%20and%20has%20side%20effects%2C%26quot%3B%20Maier%20told%20reporter%20Hilary%20Brueck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Supplements%20aren't%20regulated%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESupplements%20are%20not%20regulated%20as%20strictly%20as%20prescription%20medications%2C%20which%20means%20what%20you're%20actually%20getting%20might%20be%20different%20than%20what's%20listed%20on%20the%20bottle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20some%20supplements%20may%20be%20contaminated%20with%20other%20ingredients%20%E2%80%94%20a%20problem%20called%20adulteration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou'll%20be%20shocked%20at%20how%20many%20weight%20loss%20and%20dietary%20and%20bodybuilding%20supplements%20are%20adulterated%20with%20conventional%20medications%2C%26quot%3B%20Gurley%20told%20Insider%20previously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20dose%20of%20ingredients%20listed%20on%20the%20bottle%20could%20be%20different%20that%20what's%20actually%20in%20the%20capsule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Accidental%20overdose%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20both%20medications%20and%20supplements%2C%20taking%20too%20much%20can%20be%20dangerous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPopular%20longevity%20supplements%20like%20magnesium%20can%20be%20toxic%20if%20too%20much%20is%20taken.%20Signs%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Ftoo-much-magnesium%23%3A~%3Atext%3DPeople%2520taking%2520a%2520magnesium%2520supplement%2Cto%2520contact%2520your%2520doctor%2520immediately.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emagnesium%20toxicity%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20include%20muscle%20weakness%2C%20low%20blood%20pressure%2C%20and%20confusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthline.com%2Fnutrition%2Ffish-oil-side-effects%23TOC_TITLE_HDR_6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EToo%20much%20omega-3%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20linked%20to%20bleeding%20gums%2C%20low%20blood%20pressure%2C%20and%20stomach%20upset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fvitamin-d-and-longevity-anti-aging-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etoo%20much%20vitamin%20D%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20buildup%20of%20calcium%20in%20the%20heart%2C%20blood%2C%20kidneys%2C%20and%20lungs.%20In%20extreme%20cases%2C%20it%20has%20been%20reported%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC2813130%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecause%20kidney%20failure%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Beware%20of%20side%20effects%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETechnically%20a%20medication%20and%20not%20a%20supplement%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fmetformin-diabetes-weight-loss-anti-aging-drug-long-covid-prevention-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emetformin%3