20a%20four-wheeler.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2033-year-old%2C%20who%20contested%20in%20the%20reserved%20tribal%20seat%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20the%20fledgling%20Bharat%20Adivasi%20Party%20-%20which%20was%20formed%20only%20in%20September%20this%20year%20-%20defeated%20his%20nearest%20rival%2C%20Harsh%20Vijay%20Gehlot%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20by%20a%20margin%20of%204%2C618%20votes.%20It%20was%20the%20only%20seat%20in%20the%20230-member%20Assembly%20that%20was%20won%20by%20a%20party%20other%20than%20the%20BJP%20or%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20party%20colleagues%20supported%20me%20in%20the%20campaign.%20They%20campaigned%20for%20me%20on%20an%20empty%20stomach%20and%20even%20spent%20money%20from%20their%20own%20pockets.%20I%20had%20to%20urgently%20go%20to%20the%20Bhopal%20Assembly%20to%20submit%20documents.%20No%20four-wheeler%20was%20available%2C%20and%20so%20I%20left%20on%20a%20motorcycle%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MLA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20certainly%20very%20poor%2C%20but%20I%20want%20to%20do%20good%20work%20for%20the%20disadvantaged.%20I%20will%20work%20honestly%20and%20earnestly%20to%20ensure%20the%20government's%20schemes%20are%20implemented%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BSold%20Eggs%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dodiyar%20is%20from%20the%20tribal%20community%20and%20was%20born%20in%20Radha%20Kua%20village%20in%20the%20Sailana%20constituency.%20He%20and%20his%20family%20live%20in%20a%20mud%20house%20and%20his%20mother%20said%20she%20sold%20eggs%20in%20the%20village%20and%20worked%20as%20a%20labourer%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20Rajasthan%20to%20fund%20his%20initial%20education.%20Mr%20Dodiyar%20worked%20as%20a%20labourer%20himself%20to%20complete%20his%20Bachelor%20of%20Arts%2C%20and%20delivered%20tiffins%20in%20Delhi%20while%20pursuing%20his%20LLB%20from%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20returning%20to%20his%20village%2C%20Mr%20Dodiyar%20began%20doing%20social%20work%20and%20contested%20his%20first%20election%20from%20the%20Sailana%20Assembly%20seat%20as%20an%20independent%20in%202018.%20After%20losing%20that%20year%2C%20he%20contested%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20but%20was%20defeated%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESuccess%2C%20Finally%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20two%20losses%20as%20an%20Independent%2C%20Mr%20Dodiyar%20decided%20to%20contest%20as%20a%20candidate%20from%20the%20newly%20formed%20Bharat%20Adivasi%20Party%20(BAP).%20In%20the%20November%2017%20elections%2C%20he%20got%2071%2C219%20votes%20against%20the%20Congress%20candidate's%2066%2C601%20and%20the%20BJP%20candidate's%2041%2C584.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BAP%2C%20which%20is%20a%20Rajasthan-based%20party%20and%20won%20three%20seats%20in%20that%20state%2C%20was%20formed%20by%20two%20MLAs%2C%20Rajkumar%20Roat%20and%20Ramprasad%20Dindor%2C%20in%20September%20after%20a%20split%20in%20the%20Bharatiya%20Tribal%20party.%20On%20its%20website%2C%20the%20party%20says%20it%20is%20dedicated%20to%20improving%20the%20lives%20of%20tribal%20communities%20and%20ensuring%20that%20they%20get%20access%20to%20education%2C%20healthcare%20and%20economic%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBharat%20Adivasi%20Party%20is%20very%20concerned%20about%20the%20environment.%20We%20pledge%20to%20work%20tirelessly%20to%20protect%20and%20preserve%20our%20natural%20world.%20We%20will%20support%20policies%20that%20promote%20clean%20energy%2C%20reduce%20pollution%20and%20protect%20our%20precious%20ecosystems%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20current%20and%20future%20generations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20website%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701882960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fefl1lru_kamleshwar-dodiyar_625x300_06_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradeshs-only-non-bjp-non-congress-mla-lives-in-mud-house-4640310%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20