tum%2C%20and%20yet%2C%20we're%20only%20beginning%20to%20scratch%20the%20surface%20of%20what's%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20Google%20chief%20executive%20Sundar%20Pichai%20said%20in%20a%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20new%20era%20of%20models%20represents%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20science%20and%20engineering%20efforts%20we've%20undertaken%20as%20a%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20first%20AI%20model%20to%20outperform%20human%20experts%20in%20certain%20benchmarks%20involving%20problem%20solving%2C%20math%2C%20physics%2C%20history%2C%20law%2C%20medicine%20and%20ethics%2C%20Google%20DeepMind%20vice%20president%20of%20product%20Eli%20Collins%20said%20during%20a%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20demonstration%20showed%20Gemini%20recognizing%20what%20it%20was%20shown%2C%20from%20a%20person%20acting%20out%20a%20%26quot%3BMatrix%26quot%3B%20movie%20scene%20to%20someone%20drawing%20a%20duck%20and%20then%20holding%20up%20a%20rubber%20duck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGemini%20commented%20on%20what%20it%20was%20shown%2C%20making%20comparisons%2C%20drawing%20conclusions%2C%20and%20offering%20suggestions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerformance%20of%20an%20%26quot%3BUltra%26quot%3B%20version%20of%20Gemini%20%26quot%3Bfar%20exceeds%26quot%3B%20that%20of%20other%20state-of-the-art%20models%20in%2030%20benchmark%20tests%20measuring%20capabilities%20such%20as%20image%20understanding%20or%20mathematical%20reasoning%2C%20according%20to%20Collins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%26quot%3BPro%26quot%3B%20version%20of%20Gemini%20built%20into%20Bard%20is%20designed%20to%20handle%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20tasks.%20A%20%26quot%3BNano%26quot%3B%20version%20is%20tailored%20for%20smartphones%2C%20coming%20first%20to%20Google's%20top-of-the-line%20Pixel%208%20handset.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle%20raced%20out%20its%20own%20Bard%20chatbot%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20continually%20updating%20the%20chatbot%20based%20on%20people's%20feedback%2C%20according%20to%20Bard%20vice%20president%20Sissie%20Hsiao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20that%20rapid%20innovation%20is%20bringing%20us%20to%20what%20we%20see%20as%20a%20truly%20transformative%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20Hsiao%20said%20during%20the%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20Gemini%2C%20Bard%20is%20getting%20its%20biggest%20upgrade%20yet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20collaborator%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBard%20will%20use%20Gemini%20for%20more%20advanced%20reasoning%2C%20planning%2C%20and%20understanding%20capabilities%2C%20a%20demonstration%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20available%20in%20English%20in%20more%20than%20170%20countries%20and%20territories%2C%20with%20more%20languages%20added%20soon%2C%20according%20to%20Hsiao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGemini-infused%20Bard%20will%20be%20expanded%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bmulti-modal%2C%26quot%3B%20meaning%20it%20will%20be%20able%20to%20work%20with%20auditory%20and%20visual%20input%20as%20well%20as%20text%20prompts%2C%20executives%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20Gemini%20we%20are%20one%20step%20closer%20to%20our%20vision%20of%20bringing%20you%20the%20best%20AI%20collaborator%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Hsiao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGemini%20ramps%20up%20the%20quality%20of%20Bard's%20performance%2C%20whether%20in%20writing%20poetry%20or%20computer%20code%20to%20shopping%20queries%20or%20research%20projects%2C%20according%20to%20Hsiao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BUltra%26quot%3B%20version%20of%20Gemini%20designed%20to%20handle%20highly%20complex%20tasks%20will%20be%20released%20early%20next%20year%2C%20Google%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20in%20awe%20of%20what%20it's%20capable%20of%2C%26quot%3B%20Collins%20said%20of%20Gemini.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20start%20of%20a%20new%20era%20for%20us%20at%20Google%20as%20we%20continue%20to%20rapidly%20innovate%20and%20advance%20the%20model's%20capabilities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogl