1701879185000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105790871%2Cimgsize-645366.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fus-navy-downed-drone-originating-from-houthi-controlled-part-of-yemen-official%2Farticleshow%2F105790873.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105790873.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fus-navy-downed-drone-originating-from-houthi-controlled-part-of-yemen-official%2Farticleshow%2F105790873.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indonesian%20Rescue%20Team%20Finds%20Body%20Of%20Last%20Missing%20Hiker%20On%20Volcano%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20hiker%20missing%20after%20a%20volcanic%20eruption%20on%20Indonesia's%20Mount%20Marapi%20was%20found%20dead%20today%2C%20rescuers%20said.%20According%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-67634503%5C%22%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3Ereport%2C%20the%20final%20hiker's%20body%20was%C2%A0recovered%20on%20Wednesday%20by%20Indonesia's%20National%20Search%20and%20Rescue%20Agency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''The%20joint%20search%20and%20rescue%20team%20has%20found%20one%20victim%20of%20the%20Mount%20Marapi%20eruption%2C%20who%20is%20now%20in%20the%20process%20of%20being%20evacuated%2C''%20Abdul%20Malik%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Padang%20Search%20and%20Rescue%20Agency%2C%20told%20reporters%20on%20Wednesday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBasarnas%2C%20the%20national%20search%20and%20rescue%20agency%2C%20earlier%20identified%20the%20final%20hiker%20as%20a%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Mount%20Marapi%20on%20the%20island%20of%20Sumatra%20spewed%20an%20ash%20tower%203%2C000%20metres%20(9%2C800%20feet)%20--%20taller%20than%20the%20volcano%20itself%20--%20into%20the%20sky%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20rescuers%20worked%20for%20days%20to%20find%20the%20missing%20hikers%2C%20who%20had%20been%20carried%20down%20the%20mountain%20in%20bodybags%20in%20an%20arduous%20search%20effort%20hampered%20by%20further%20eruptions%20and%20bad%20weather%20that%20forced%20workers%20to%20intermittently%20take%20shelter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%2075%20hikers%20on%20the%20mountain%20during%20the%20eruption%20were%20found%20alive%20and%20carried%20down%2C%20with%20multiple%20suffering%20burns%20and%20fractures.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20dead%20were%20carried%20down%20the%20mountain%20in%20bodybags%20over%20several%20days%2C%20rescue%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndonesia%20experiences%20frequent%20seismic%20and%20volcanic%20activity%20due%20to%20its%20position%20on%20the%20Pacific%20%26quot%3BRing%20of%20Fire%26quot%3B%2C%20where%20tectonic%20plates%20collide.%C2%A0Mount%20Marapi%2C%20which%20means%20%26quot%3BMountain%20of%20Fire%26quot%3B%2C%20is%20the%20most%20active%20volcano%20on%20Sumatra%20Island%20and%20one%20of%20the%20archipelago's%20nearly%20130%20active%20volcanoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20monitoring%20the%20volcano%20detected%20at%20least%20five%20more%20eruptions%20on%20December%205%20as%20the%20search%20went%20on.%C2%A0Fifty-two%20people%20were%20rescued%20since%20the%20eruption%20and%20some%20of%20the%20survivors%20have%20described%20their%20panic%20after%20it%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20zig-zagging%2C%20going%20down%20around%2030%20to%2040%20metres%26quot%3B%20to%20a%20trekking%20post%2C%20Ridho%2C%2022%2C%20told%20AFP%20from%20a%20bed%20in%20a%20nearby%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20eruption%20sounded%20loud%2C%20I%20took%20a%20look%20behind%20and%20then%20immediately%20ran%20away%20as%20everyone%20did.%20Some%20jumped%20and%20fell.%20I%20took%20cover%20behind%20the%20rocks%2C%20there%20were%20no%20trees%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701878880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fdbucq48g_mount-marapi-rescue-op-afp_625x300_06_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmount-marapi-indonesian-rescue-team-finds-body-of-last-missing-hiker-on-volcano-4640319%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Basarnas%2C%20the%20national%20search%20and%20rescue%20agency%2C%20earlier%20identified%20the%20final%20hiker%20as%20a%20woman.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmount-marapi-indonesian-rescue-team-finds-body-of-last-missing-hiker-on-volcano-4640319%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmount-marapi-indonesian-rescue-team-finds-body-of-last-missing-hiker-on-volcano-4640319%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmount-marapi-indonesian-rescue-team-finds-body-of-last-missing-hiker-on-volcano-4640319%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pro-Kremlin%20Ukrainian%20politician%20found%20dead%20near%20Moscow%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701878846000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105790802%2Cimgsize-1477632.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fpro-kremlin-ukrainian-politician-found-dead-near-moscow%2Farticleshow%2F105790665.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105790665.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fpro-kremlin-ukrainian-politician-found-dead-near-moscow%2Farticleshow%2F105790665.cms%22%2C