%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fsacked-suella-braverman-warns-uk-pm-rishi-sunak-of-electoral-oblivion%2Farticleshow%2F105790725.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20First%20Post-Poll%20Huddle%2C%20Opposition%20Meets%20At%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge's%20Home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20while%20cancelling%20the%20mega%20meeting%20of%20its%20top%20leaders%20today%2C%20had%20a%20dinner%20meet%20of%20its%20floor%20leaders%20at%20the%20house%20of%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge.%20The%20big%20meeting%20was%20postponed%20to%20the%20third%20week%20of%20December%20after%20several%20key%20leaders%2C%20including%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20said%20they%20were%20not%20available%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFloor%20leaders%20of%2017%20parties%20met%20this%20evening%20and%20discussed%20steps%20to%20improve%20coordination%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Among%20those%20present%20at%20the%20hour-long%20meet%20were%20Congress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20Pramod%20Tiwari%2C%20K%20C%20Venugopal%20and%20Jairam%20Ramesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20leaders%20present%20included%20Mahua%20Majhi%20of%20JMM%2C%20Vaiko%20of%20MDMK%2C%20NK%20Premchandran%20of%20RSP%2C%20Binoy%20Viswam%20of%20CPI%2C%20Lalan%20Singh%20of%20JDU%2C%20Ram%20Gopal%20Yadav%20and%20ST%20Hasan%20of%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%20of%20RLD%2C%20AAP's%20Raghav%20Chadha%2C%20Vandana%20Chavan%20of%20NCP%20and%20Tiruchi%20Siva%20of%20DMK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElamaram%20Kareem%20of%20CPM%2C%20Faiyaz%20Ahmad%20of%20RJD%2C%20Jose%20K%20Mani%20of%20Kerala%20Congress%20(M)%2C%20Javed%20Ali%20Khan%20of%20SP%2C%20TR%20Baalu%20of%20DMK%2C%20Hasnain%20Masoodi%20of%20NC%20and%20Mohd%20Basheer%20of%20IUML%20also%20attended%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata%20Banerjee's%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20meet%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday's%20meeting%20was%20called%20by%20the%20Congress%20after%20its%20defeat%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20three%20heartland%20states%20--%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20--%20in%20the%20recently%20concluded%20assembly%20polls.%20Opposition%20leaders%2C%20however%2C%20said%20it%20was%20not%20a%20defeat%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defeat%20has%20drawn%20focus%20on%20the%20Congress%20refusal%20to%20share%20seats%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Leaders%20from%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%2C%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20Omar%20Abdullah's%20National%20Conference%20have%20said%20the%20Congress%20should%20be%20more%20accommodating%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20its%20regional%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alliance%20arrangement%20is%20expected%20to%20work%20on%20a%20one-on-one%20basis%2C%20meaning%20only%20one%20Opposition%20candidate%20will%20be%20fielded%20against%20a%20BJP%20candidate.%20This%20would%20work%20only%20if%20all%20parties%20in%20the%20bloc%20respect%20the%20arrangement%20and%20be%20ready%20to%20step%20down%20when%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20assembly%20polls%20out%20of%20the%20way%2C%20discussions%20on%20seat-sharing%20are%20expected%20to%20begin%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20at%20least%2026%20parties%20came%20together%20to%20form%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20to%20take%20on%20the%20BJP%20in%20what%20they%20call%20a%20%26quot%3Bdo-or-die%26quot%3B%20election.%20So%20far%2C%20they%20have%20held%20three%20rounds%20of%20talks%20in%20Patna%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701878220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fc228r86k_india-meet-rahul-gandhi-kharge_625x300_06_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%2