pied%20Kashmir%20In%20Lok%20Sabha%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwenty%20four%20seats%20have%20been%20reserved%20in%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Assembly%20for%20the%20Pakistan%20Occupied%20Kashmir%20as%20%26quot%3BPoK%20is%20ours%2C%26quot%3B%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20in%20Parliament%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETabling%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reorganisation%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20that%20earlier%2C%20Jammu%20had%2037%20seats%20but%20now%20it%20has%2043%2C%20while%20Kashmir%20had%2046%20seats%2C%20now%20it%20has%2047%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20Delimitation%20Commission%2C%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20the%20delimitation%20of%20asssembly%20and%20parliamentary%20constituencies%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20has%20reserved%2024%20seats%20for%20PoK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Delimitation%20(Commission)%20went%20everywhere%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%20The%20representatives%20of%20several%20communities%2C%20including%20Kashmiri%20migrants%20and%20people%20displaced%20in%20PoK%2C%20had%20submitted%20applications%20to%20them%20regarding%20their%20representation%20in%20state%20assembly.%20I%20am%20happy%20that%20the%20commission%20has%20taken%20cognizance%20of%20this%20and%20the%20(then)%20Election%20Commissioner%20of%20India%20has%20nominated%20two%20seats%20in%20state%20assembly%20for%20Kashmiri%20migrants%20and%20one%20seat%20for%20a%20person%20displaced%20in%20PoK%2C%20which%20has%20been%20occupied%20unauthorizedly%20by%20Pakistan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarlier%20there%20were%2037%20seats%20in%20Jammu%20(division)%2C%20now%20there%20are%2043.%20Earlier%20there%20were%2046%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20now%20there%20are%2047.%20And%2024%20seats%20for%20PoK%20have%20been%20reserved%2C%20%3Cem%3EKyuki%20Woh%20Hamara%20Hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(because%20PoK%20is%20ours)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20minister%20said%20that%20now%20there%20will%20be%20five%20nominated%20members%20in%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20was%20speaking%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20during%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reservation%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%20and%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reorganisation%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarlier%20two%20women%20were%20nominated%20by%20the%20Governor%20in%20state%20assembly.%20And%20now%2C%20two%20of%20the%20Kashmiri%20migrants%2C%20out%20of%20whom%20one%20of%20must%20be%20a%20woman%2C%20and%20one%20person%20from%20PoK%2C%20will%20be%20nominated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20debate%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20also%20said%20that%20these%20bills%20pertain%20to%20bringing%20justice%20to%20those%20against%20whom%20injustice%20was%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%2C%20as%20per%20figures%2C%20around%2046%2C631%20families%20and%201%2C57%2C967%20people%20were%20displaced%20in%20their%20own%20country.%20%26quot%3BThis%20bill%20is%20to%20give%20them%20rights%20and%20representation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701877920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F16h3bv1k_amit-shah-parliament_625x300_06_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpok-is-ours-amit-shah-in-parliament-24-seats-reserved-in-jammu-and-kashmir-for-pok-4639836%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Twenty%20four%20seats%20have%20been%20reserved%20in%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Assembly%20for%20the%20Pakistan%20Occupied%20Kashmir%20as%20%26quot%3BPoK%20is%20ours%2C%26quot%3B%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20in%20the%20Parliament%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author