lwama%2C%20a%20Teacher%20Facilitates%20the%20Return%20of%20Migrant%20Workers'%20Bodies%20to%20Their%20Families%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06170500%2Fimage-1580.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPulwama%20(Kashmir)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOn%20October%2030%2C%20a%20migrant%20labourer%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fkashmir-pulwama-migrant-labourer-shot-militants-9005663%2F%5C%22%3Eshot%20dead%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20unidentified%20militants%20in%20South%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Pulwama%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%2C%20Mukesh%20Kumar%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20Nowpora%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20took%20place%20a%20day%20after%20the%20Resistance%20Front%20(RTF)%2C%20an%20offshoot%20of%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-cop-attacked-by-terrorists-srinagar-injured-dead-2455276-2023-10-29%5C%22%3Eshot%20at%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20police%20inspector%20while%20he%20was%20off%20duty%20in%20Srinagar.%20He%20was%20grievously%20injured%20and%20was%20admitted%20to%20a%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20such%20a%20volatile%20environment%2C%20Mukesh%2C%20along%20with%2015%20others%2C%20came%20to%20Pulwama%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Purwa%20to%20earn%20a%20better%20wage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20just%20hours%20after%20finishing%20his%20job%2C%20he%20was%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajesh%20Kumar%2C%20one%20of%20the%2015%20men%20who%20had%20come%20all%20the%20way%20from%20UP%2C%20recalled%20how%20he%20kept%20urging%20Mukesh%20not%20to%20venture%20out%20alone%2C%20even%20if%20it%20meant%20sending%20money%20home.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20wanted%20to%20send%20money%20urgently%20to%20his%20wife%20and%20four%20children.%20His%20desperation%20led%20him%20to%20his%20death%20like%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwenty-eight%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2FgetFile%2Floksabhaquestions%2Fannex%2F179%2FAU1421.pdf%3Fsource%3Dpqals%5C%22%3Emigrant%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20been%20killed%20since%202017%2C%20according%20to%20government%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20identifying%20Mukesh%E2%80%99s%20body%2C%20his%20fellow%20colleagues%20were%20taken%20to%20a%20safe%20house%2C%20where%20they%20wondered%20how%20to%20send%20his%20body%20back%20to%20his%20family%20in%20Purwa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20problem%20was%20solved%20when%20Faisal%20Parray%2C%20a%20school%20teacher%20and%20resident%20of%20Pulwama%2C%20stepped%20in%20to%20help%20transport%20Mukesh%E2%80%99s%20body%20back%20to%20Purwa.%20Parray%20also%20assisted%20in%20getting%20the%20body%20embalmed%20to%20ensure%20that%20Mukesh%20would%20be%20received%20by%20his%20family%20in%20an%20undecayed%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202022%2C%20he%20has%20voluntarily%20helped%20facilitate%20the%20return%20of%20at%20least%2020%20migrants%20who%20had%20died%20in%20the%20valley%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20know%20his%20name.%20He%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20part%20of%20the%20police%20or%20the%20army.%20Yet%20he%20helped%20us%20through%20his%20own%20sources%20and%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rajesh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20know%20how%20painful%20it%20is%2C%20firstly%2C%20to%20lose%20someone%20and%20secondly%2C%20to%20run%20from%20pillar%20to%20post%20to%20obtain%20their%20body%20and%20send%20it%20back%20to%20their%20hometown%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Parray%2C%20recalling%20his%20trauma%20of%20losing%20a%20loved%20one%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20he%20had%20helped%20Deepsha%20Dey%2C%20who%20lost%20her%20father%2C%20Pradeep%20Kumar%20Dey%2C%20during%20a%20vacation%20in%20the%20valley.%20The%20road%20accident%20occurred%20on%20May%2025%2C%202023%2C%20on%20NH44%20near%20Awantipora.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParray%20facilitated%20the%20local%20transfer%20of%20the%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDey%20also%20credited%20the%20local%20police%20for%20assisting%20her%20at%20every%20step%2C%20even%20when%20the%20death%20certificate%20of%20her%20father%20had%20a%20spelling%20error.%20She%20remembered%20how%20helpful%20the%20locals%20were%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20decided%20to%20donate%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20body%20to%20a%20local%20anatomy%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Nasir%20Raza%20found%20himself%20trapped%20in%20a%20similar%20situation%20when%20his%20cousin%20Zahid%20Ahmed%2C%20a%20labourer%2C%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20road%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2026%2C%20Ahmed%20and%20his%20relative%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20road%20accident%20near%20Pulwama%20while%20being%20transported%20to%20a%20work%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaza%2C%20who%20was%20called%20after%20his%20relatives%20passed%20away%2C%20had%20to%20establish%20the%20identity%20of%20Ahmed%2C%20who%20had%20no%20documents%20linked%20to%20him%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20got%20a%20call%20from%20the%20police%20in%20Kashmir%20that%20my%20brother%20had%20died%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20document%20to%20confirm%20that%20it%20was%2C%20by%20all%20possibilities%2C%20my%20own%20brother.%20With%20this%2C%20Faisal%20%5BParray%5D%20sir%20reached%20out%20to%20me.%20He%20helped%20me%20understand%20the%20ways%20in%20which%20we%20could%20ascertain%20my%20brother%E2%80%99s%20identity%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raza%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20explained%20that%20for%20two%20days%20after%20the%20deaths%2C%20both%20bodies%20remained%20in%20Kashmir%20because%20their%20identities%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20confirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaza%20also%20shared%20how%2C%20at%20his%20own%20expense%2C%20Parray%20sent%20the%20bodies%20of%20Ahmed%20and%20the%20other%20relative%20to%20Delhi.%20He%20also%20arranged%20for%20an%20ambulance%20that%20transported%20Raza%20and%20the%20bodies%20of%20his%20relatives%20from%20the%20airport%20in%20Delhi%20to%20Bareilly.%20From%20there%2C%20they%20took%20a%20vehicle%20to%20reach%20their%20hometown%2C%20Bisalpur%2C%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20senior%20police%20officer%20motivated%20Parray%20to%20undertake%20this%20voluntary%20work%2C%20Parray%20personally%20funds%20the%20assistance%20provided%20to%20these%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSeeking%20reimbursement%20from%20the%20authorities%20is%20a%20tough%20task%2C%20and%20the%20process%20is%20slow.%20But%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20me%20from%20helping%20the%20helpless%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parray%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701864006000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06170500%2Fimage-1580.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fin-kashmirs-pulwama-a-teacher-facilitates-the-return-of-migrant-workers-bodies-to-their-families%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%202022%2C%20Faisal%20Parray%20has%20voluntarily%20assisted%20in%20facilitating%20the%20return%20of%20at%20least%2020%20migrants%20who%20died%20in%20the%20valley%20back%20home.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fin-kashmirs-pulwama-a-teacher-facilitates-the-return-of-migrant-workers-bodies-to-their-families%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Attempted%20murder%20charges%20dropped%20against%20pilot%20who%20'tried%20to%20cut%20plane's%20engines'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701863280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2Fskynews-alaska-pilot-emerson_6333289.jpg%3F20231024031132%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fjoseph-emerson-attempted-murder-charges-dropped-against-pilot-who-tried-to-cut-engines-13024067%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20Alaska%2