van%20Day%20of%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20on%20December%206%2C%20just%20a%20few%20days%20after%20the%20election%20results%20for%20state%20assemblies%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Mizoram%20were%20declared%20and%20the%20impartiality%20and%20fairness%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20(EC)%20in%20conducting%20elections%20was%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeventy-seven%20years%20after%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20passing%20away%2C%20his%20apprehensions%20that%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20provision%20in%20the%20Constitution%20preventing%20the%20executive%20to%20appoint%20a%20foolish%2C%20knave%20or%20a%20pliable%20person%20as%20election%20commissioner%20or%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20%E2%80%93%20making%20the%20EC%2C%20in%20his%20words%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20thumb%20of%20the%20executive%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20have%20come%20true.%20He%20said%20so%20in%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20on%20June%2016%2C%201949%2C%20during%20the%20debates%20on%20the%20draft%20Article%20289%20(now%20Article%20324)%20of%20the%20Constitution%20dealing%20with%20the%20EC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHas%20not%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20EC%20in%20the%20conduct%20of%20elections%20to%20the%20aforementioned%20state%20assemblies%20testified%20to%20the%20apprehensions%20of%20Ambedkar%20that%20it%20would%20come%20under%20the%20thumb%20of%20the%20executive%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20was%20in%20operation%20and%20election%20campaign%20was%20at%20its%20peak%2C%20the%20EC%20did%20not%20prevent%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20when%20it%20released%20money%20to%20the%20people%20under%20the%20Ladli%20Behena%20scheme.%20In%20contrast%20it%20prevented%20the%20Telangana%20government%20from%20releasing%20money%20to%20farmers%20under%20the%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20Scheme.%20It%20clearly%20proved%20the%20point%20that%20the%20standard%20employed%20by%20the%20EC%20for%20BJP%20state%20governments%20was%20not%20applied%20to%20the%20Telangana%20government.%20The%20glaring%20differentiation%20in%20applying%20one%20norm%20for%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20in%20MP%20and%20the%20non-application%20of%20the%20same%20norm%20for%20Telangana%20is%20evocative%20of%20the%20doctrine%20of%20differential%20rights%20often%20employed%20by%20the%20colonial%20rulers%20in%20India%20to%20discriminate%20against%20Indians%20and%20favour%20the%20whites%20who%20wielded%20power.%20It%20is%20tragic%20that%20the%20same%20doctrine%20is%20in%20operation%20in%20the%20action%20of%20EC%2C%20which%20in%20the%20words%20of%20Ambedkar%20has%20%E2%80%9Ccome%20under%20the%20thumb%20of%20the%20executive%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmbedkar%E2%80%99s%20apprehensions%20resonated%20in%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbedkar%E2%80%99s%20apprehension%20expressed%20in%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20in%201949%20was%20also%20reflected%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20which%20in%20its%20judgement%20of%20March%202%2C%202023%20prescribed%20a%20group%20consisting%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20chief%20justice%20of%20India%20and%20leader%20of%20opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20to%20select%20members%20of%20EC%20so%20that%20it%20is%20not%20reduced%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Cservile%20commission%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Ambedkar%20while%20moving%20the%20draft%20Article%20289%20in%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20on%20June%2015%2C%201949%20for%20setting%20up%20an%20Election%20Commission%2C%20had%20said%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%5BW%5Dithout%20any%20kind%20of%20dissent%2C%20that%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20purity%20and%20freedom%20of%20elections%20to%20the%20legislative%20bodies%2C%20it%20was%20of%20utmost%20importance%20that%20they%20should%20be%20freed%20from%20any%20kind%20of%20interference%20from%20the%20executive%20of%20the%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20EC%20only%20issued%20notices%20to%20some%20opposition%20leaders%20on%20the%20charge%20that%20they%20violated%20the%20MCC%20and%20completely%20ignored%20the%20complaints%20of%20opposition%20parties%20against%20BJP%20leaders%20including%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20for%20invoking%20religion%20for%20seeking%20votes%20clearly%20proved%20the%20point%20that%20the%20EC%20did%20not%20act%20impartially.%20It%20is%20in%20such%20tragic%20circumstances%20that%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20cautionary%20words%20assume%20critical%20significance%20for%20summoning%20the%20collective%20energy%20for%20addressing%20the%20problem%20caused%20by%20the%20EC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intervention%20of%20the%20courts%2C%20in%20particular%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20in%20this%20regard%20is%20of%20utmost%20importance.%20The%20Modi%20government%20has%20prepared%20a%20Bill%20overturning%20the%20aforementioned%20order%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20by%20replacing%20the%20CJI%20in%20the%20collegium-like%20committee%20to%20select%20members%20of%20the%20EC%20with%20a%20nominee%20to%20be%20appointed%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20It%20means%20that%20it%20wants%20to%20play%20out%20the%20apprehensions%20of%20Ambedkar%20that%20the%20EC%20would%20come%20%E2%80%9Cunder%20the%20thumb%20of%20the%20executive%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmbedkar%E2%80%99s%20apprehensions%20on%20boycott%20of%20minorities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20solemn%20occasion%20of%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20death%20anniversary%2C%20it%20is%20instructive%20to%20see%20in%20retrospect%20his%20draft%20Constitution%20for%20the%20United%20States%20of%20India.%20He%20prepared%20it%20in%201945%20and%20submitted%20it%20to%20a%20sub-committee%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly.%20Anticipating%20that%20minorities%20in%20India%20would%20be%20boycotted%20in%20the%20social%20and%20economic%20realms%20on%20account%20of%20the%20discrimination%20meted%20out%20to%20them%20because%20of%20their%20faith%2C%20he%20dealt%20with%20the%20issue%20very%20elaborately%20and%20provided%20a%20separate%20section%20under%20the%20captions%20%E2%80%9CProvisions%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20minorities%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cprotection%20against%20social%20boycott.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20defined%20boycott%20in%20very%20broad%20terms%2C%20which%20is%20applicable%20for%20our%20times%20marked%20by%20calls%20issued%20by%20several%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20many%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Edharma%20sansads%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20or%20Religious%20Parliaments%20for%20boycott%20of%20Muslims%20so%20that%20their%20exclusion%20from%20social%20and%20economic%20fields%20are%20ensured.%20He%20also%20dealt%20with%20measures%20which%20would%20amount%20to%20instigation%20and%20promotion%20of%20boycott%20and%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhoever%20publicly%20makes%20or%20publishes%20or%20circulates%20a%20proposal%20for%20or%20makes%2C%20publishes%20or%20circulates%20any%20statement%2C%20rumour%20or%20report%20with%20intent%20to%2C%20or%20which%20he%20has%20reason%20to%20believe%20to%20be%20likely%20to%20cause%2C%20or%20in%20any%20other%20way%20instigates%20or%20promotes%20the%20boycotting%20of%20any%20person%20or%20class%20of%20persons%2C%20shall%20be%20guilty%20of%20the%20offence%20of%20instigating%20or%20promoting%20a%20boycott.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20farsighted%20when%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20these%20offences%20shall%20be%20deemed%20to%20be%20cognisable%20offences%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Union%20legislature%20shall%20make%20laws%20prescribing%20punishment%20for%20these%20offences%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETragically%20inside%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20a%20constituent%20of%20the%20Union%20legislature%2C%20a%20BJP%20member%2C%20hurled%20abuses%20against%20another%20MP%20on%20account%20of%20his%20faith%20and%20no%20penal%20action%20has%20so%20far%20been%20taken%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20measures%20provided%20by%20Ambedkar%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20existential%20crises%20confronting%20our%20republic%20are%20of%20critical%20significance%20for%2021st-century%20India.%20Remaining%20sensitive%20to%20his%20concerns%20and%20taking%20remedial%20action%20for%20safeguarding%20the%20Constitution%20would%20constitute%20true%20tribute%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ES.N.%20Sahu%20served%20as%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20to%20President%20of%20India%20K.R.%20Narayanan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701861645000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F14124741%2FIMG_1874-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fb-r-ambedkars-fears-on-the-ecs-independence-boycott-of-minorities-are-coming-true%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Election%20Commission's%20actions%20during%20the%20recent%20state%20assembly%20elections%20suggest%20that%20Ambedkar's%20warning%20%E2%80%93%20that%20it%20may%20come%20under%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20thumb%20of%20the%20executive%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20was%20well%20placed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fb-r-ambedkars-fears-on-the-ecs-independence-boycott-of-minorities-are-coming-true%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22British%20financier%20extradited%20to%20Denmark%20over%20%241.7bn%20tax%20fraud%20charges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701861300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F768x432%2Fskynews-sanjay-shah-elysium_6384000.jpg%3F20231206112300%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbritish-financier-sanjay-shah-facing-charges-over-17bn-fraud-extradited-to-denmark-from-uae-13024051%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Dubai-based%20British%20hedge%20fund%20trader%20accused%20of%20orchestrating%20a%20%241.7bn%20(%C2%A31.34bn)%20tax%20fraud%20has%20been%20extradited%20to%20Denmark.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A56%2C%22canonicalUrl%