%20For%20that%2C%20the%20party%20will%20have%20to%20tame%20its%20internal%20demons%3B%20otherwise%2C%20it%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20inspire%20any%20confidence%20among%20its%20prospective%20allies%2C%20leave%20alone%20the%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F04192003%2Fstatecraft.png%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-237577%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22233%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20undeniable%20but%20also%20unfortunate%20that%20despite%20the%20drubbing%20the%20party%20has%20received%20from%20voters%2C%20the%202023%20campaign%20has%20reinforced%20the%20centrality%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20in%20the%20Congress%20scheme%20of%20things.%20This%20round%20of%20elections%20saw%20the%20emergence%20of%20Priyanka%20Gandhi-Vadra%20as%20a%20star%20campaigner%2C%20who%20earned%20the%20party%20leaders%E2%80%99%20admiration%20as%20the%20most%20effective%20communicator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20contrast%2C%20Congress%20president%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20has%2C%20disappointingly%20enough%2C%20refused%20to%20explore%20the%20potential%20and%20power%20of%20his%20office.%20For%20a%20while%2C%20it%20looked%20like%20he%20could%20be%20an%C2%A0%20ideal%20prime%20ministerial%20mascot%20of%20the%20Congress%3B%20but%2C%20he%20has%20just%C2%A0%20been%20content%20to%20look%20to%20%E2%80%9C10%20Janpath%E2%80%9D%20for%20inspiration%20and%20instructions.%20He%20does%20not%20command%20the%20attention%2C%20leave%20alone%20loyalty%2C%20of%20any%20of%20the%20office-bearers%20at%20the%20AICC.%20The%20Gandhi%20family%E2%80%99s%20stranglehold%20over%20the%20Congress%20remains%20complete%20and%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20entire%20non-BJP%20political%20crowd%20has%20no%20option%20but%20to%20learn%20to%20do%20business%20with%2C%20what%20is%20mockingly%20called%2C%20the%20BBC%20or%20the%20bhai-behen%20company.%20An%20even%20more%20central%20and%20pertinent%20question%20is%20whether%20the%20brother%20and%20sister%20are%20determined%2C%20even%20ruthless%20enough%2C%20to%20jettison%20their%20mother%E2%80%99s%20model%20of%20leadership%20%E2%80%93%20a%20model%20that%20has%20completely%20hollowed%20out%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20organisational%20vitality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsonia-gandhis-troubled-legacy%5C%22%3ESonia%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Troubled%20Legacy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sonia%20model%20of%20control%20was%20a%20kind%20of%20appeasement%20of%20senior%20leaders%2C%20in%20the%20states%20and%20at%20the%20central%20level.%20In%20exchange%20for%20acknowledging%20the%20Gandhi%20family%E2%80%99s%20suzerainty%2C%20these%20leaders%20were%20left%20to%20run%20their%20own%20fiefdoms.%20That%20model%20functioned%20well%2C%20though%20for%20a%20while.%20It%20ran%20into%20rough%20weather%20when%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20anointed%20heir%20apparent%2C%20but%20the%20transfer%20of%20power%20never%20took%20place.%20There%20was%20no%20regime%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20half-way%20house%20produced%20its%20own%20dysfunctionality%3B%20%E2%80%9Cyoung%E2%80%9D%20Rahul%20could%20not%20effect%20the%20changes%20he%20wanted.%20Specifically%2C%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20shuffle%20the%20old%20guard%20out.%20An%20undeclared%20civil%20war%20between%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20and%20the%20Congress%20organisation%20ate%20into%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20espirit%20de%20corps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20Rahul%20and%20Priyanka%20have%20clawed%20their%20way%20back%20to%20dominance.%20While%20this%20is%20not%20necessarily%20a%20healthy%20or%20desirable%20development%2C%20it%20is%20a%20given%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20%E2%80%93%20as%20well%20as%20the%20non-BJP%20leadership%20%E2%80%93%20will%20have%20to%20learn%20to%20work%20around%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20the%20brother%20and%20sister%20duo%20need%20to%20demonstrate%20that%20they%20can%20move%20away%20%E2%80%93%20and%20move%20away%20decisively%20%E2%80%93%20from%20their%20mother%E2%80%99s%20crowd.%20In%20the%20next%20two%20weeks%20they%20should%20replace%20the%20leadership%20matrix%20lock%2C%20stock%2C%20and%20barrel%20in%20the%20Hindi-heartland.%20In%20place%20of%20the%20tired%20and%20jaded%20faces%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Kamal%20Naths%2C%20the%20Digvijay%20Singhs%2C%20the%20Ashok%20Gehlots%2C%20the%20Bhupesh%20Baghels%20%E2%80%93%20they%20should%20hand%20over%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20reins%20to%20younger%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Telangana%20has%20shown%2C%20anyone%20sufficiently%20empowered%20and%20motivated%20can%20deliver.%20Equally%20important%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20that%20the%20brother%20and%20sister%20stop%20functioning%20as%20a%20faction%20in%20their%20own%20party.%20The%20Congress%20voter%20needs%20to%20see%20a%20cohesive%20and%20competent%20party%20at%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06152223%2Fimage-1578.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221112%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06152223%2Fimage-1578.png%201112w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06152223%2Fimage-1578-300x188.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06152223%2Fimage-1578-1024x642.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687948%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22697%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECongress%20leaders%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi-Vadra%20with%20Revanth%20Reddy.%20Photo%3A%20X%40RahulGandhi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthree-things-bjps-definitive-victory-in-the-assembly-elections-tells-us%5C%22%3EThree%20Things%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Definitive%20Victory%20in%20the%20Assembly%20Elections%20Tells%20Us%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20less%20urgent%20is%20the%20need%20for%20the%20Rahul-Priyanka%20leadership%20to%20understand%20the%20limits%20to%20their%20acceptability%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20electorate%20is%20just%20getting%20over%20its%20resentment%20of%20the%20younger%20Gandhis%E2%80%99%20sense%20of%20entitlement%2C%20though%20Robert%20Vadra%20keeps%20popping%20up%20irritatingly%2C%20from%20time%20to%20time.%20And%2C%20it%20goes%20without%20saying%2C%20that%20as%20long%20as%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20continues%20to%20make%20electoral%20politics%20into%20a%20personal%20gladiatorial%20contest%20with%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20the%20outcome%20will%20not%20be%20different%20than%20what%20it%20has%20been%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20necessary%20corollary%20is%20that%20the%20Congress%20will%20have%20to%20necessarily%20concede%20ground%20to%20the%20other%20partners%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%20To%20begin%20with%2C%20the%20convenorship%20of%20INDIA%20should%20be%20formalised%20in%20favour%20of%20Sharad%20Pawar%20or%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20or%20Nitish%20Kumar.%20The%20romantic%20notion%20of%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cchairperson%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20non-BJP%20alliance%20is%20today%20stranded%20in%20irrelevance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20extent%20that%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20remains%20crucial%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20Congress%20must%20learn%20to%20accept%20that%20%E2%80%9CUP%20is%20not%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20kingdom.%E2%80%9D%20It%20is%20imperative%20for%20Priyanka%20to%20internalise%20the%20fact%20that%20UP%2C%20like%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%2C%20has%20moved%20on%20and%20is%20no%20longer%20enamoured%20of%20her%20family%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20and%20sacrifices.%20And%2C%20if%20she%20has%20even%20an%20iota%20of%20familiarity%20with%20reality%2C%20she%20should%20be%20prepared%20to%20work%20to%20bring%20Mayawati%20into%20conversation%20and%20devise%20a%20modus%20vivendi%20between%20her%20and%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party.%20On%20its%20part%2C%20the%20Congress%20does%20not%20deserve%20more%20than%20two%20seats%20in%20any%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%20in%20the%20state.%20Her%20challenge%20is%20to%20do%20whatever%20it%20takes%20to%20deny%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20the%20Modi-Yogi%20brand.%20This%20means%20that%20for%20now%20she%20will%20need%20to%20prioritise%20a%20change%20of%20regime%20in%20New%20Delhi%20over%20and%20above%20her%20personal%20quest%20for%20glory%20and%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdmittedly%2C%20the%20Congress%20vote%20share%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20is%20nothing%20to%20snigger%20at.%20And%20that%20is%20all%20the%20more%20reason%20for%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20to%20recognise%20how%20to%20play%20the%20game%20differently%20if%20it%20at%20all%20hopes%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20non-Congress%20partners%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20would%20not%20want%20to%20rub%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20nose%20in%20the%20dirt%20of%20its%20recent%20defeat.%20The%20Congress%20leopard%20will%20not%20change%20its%20dynastic%20spots%20but%20it%20can%20be%20domesticated%20as%20a%20workable%20member%20of%20the%20hunting%20pack.%20The%20jungle%20that%20is%20Bharat%20needs%20to%20be%20claimed%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fhkhare%5C%22%3EHarish%20Khare%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20former%20editor-in-chief%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3EThe%20Tribune%3Ci%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701856803000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F25180611%2FThe-Wire-90.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fheres-what-the-congress-must-do-now-to-quickly-reset-th