0population%20of%20Gaza%2C%20more%20than%202%20million%20people%2C%20whose%20only%20lifeline%20is%20food%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHumanitarians%20must%20have%20safe%2C%20unimpeded%2C%20and%20sustained%20access%2C%20so%20we%20are%20able%20to%20distribute%20life-saving%20assistance%20throughout%20the%20territory.%20All%20parties%20must%20uphold%20their%20obligations%20under%20international%20humanitarian%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20only%20a%20lasting%20peace%20can%20end%20the%20suffering%20and%20avert%20the%20looming%20humanitarian%20catastrophe%20in%20Gaza.%20WFP%20calls%20for%20a%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%20and%20urges%20all%20leaders%20to%20work%20with%20the%20utmost%20urgency%20to%20find%20political%20solutions%20that%20can%20end%20the%20suffering%20of%20families%20on%20all%20sides%20of%20this%20harrowing%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%23%20%23%20%23%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20World%20Food%20Programme%20is%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20humanitarian%20organization%20saving%20lives%20in%20emergencies%20and%20using%20food%20assistance%20to%20build%20a%20pathway%20to%20peace%2C%20stability%20and%20prosperity%20for%20people%20recovering%20from%20conflict%2C%20disasters%20and%20the%20impact%20of%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701855042000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06132249%2FCooking-in-war.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Frenewed-fighting-in-gaza-worsen-catastrophic-hunger-crisis-un-wfp%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20World%20Food%20Programme%20has%20said%20that%20the%20distribution%20of%20food%20aid%20has%20become%20%E2%80%9Calmost%20impossible%E2%80%9D%20following%20the%20resumption%20of%20hostilities%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20on%20December%201.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Frenewed-fighting-in-gaza-worsen-catastrophic-hunger-cri